at ang iyong mga kaaway ay mas malapit.

301
00:17:33,010 --> 00:17:34,387
Hindi mo ba alam 'yan?

302
00:17:37,431 --> 00:17:39,016
Dapat kumain tayo minsan.

303
00:17:39,100 --> 00:17:40,518
Magugustuhan ko 'yan.

304
00:17:45,523 --> 00:17:47,400
Ako ito. Hindi ito sapat.

305
00:17:47,483 --> 00:17:49,402
Hukayin nang lubusan ang lahat ng iyong makakaya

306
00:17:49,485 --> 00:17:51,571
